1417257047062728705.name: Frances 'Cassandra' Coppola
1417257047062728705.content: Comparing the stablecoins of today with the free banks of the past is a category error. Stablecoin issuers are not lending against collateral, they are selling chips to punters who want to play on the crypto casino. The correct model for stablecoins is thus casinos, not banks.
